textAnnotations.description:
DID YoU
BUY SOME
NEW LAWN
STATUES,
MOM?
NO
YOUR FATHER
WENT OUTSIDE
FOR A FEW
MINUTES TO
WALK THE DOG
AND I AM JUST
BRINGING THEM
BOTH INSIDE TO
THAW OUT.
/SUB-ZERO
TEMPERATURES
